586
00:24:08,240 --> 00:24:08,940
Nian,

587
00:24:09,910 --> 00:24:11,640
Su seems young,

588
00:24:11,900 --> 00:24:13,230
but he's

589
00:24:13,720 --> 00:24:15,160
really thoughtful

590
00:24:15,350 --> 00:24:16,800
when it comes to things.

591
00:24:17,370 --> 00:24:18,400
He's a good kid.

592
00:24:19,360 --> 00:24:20,390
No, Mom,

593
00:24:20,390 --> 00:24:22,910
you've taken a liking to Su Yin after just a few words.

594
00:24:23,380 --> 00:24:24,790
