602
00:24:38,650 --> 00:24:39,250
Yes!

603
00:24:39,760 --> 00:24:40,440
Come on, Mom,

604
00:24:40,540 --> 00:24:41,350
I love you so much.

605
00:24:41,740 --> 00:24:42,620
Go ahead and eat.

606
00:24:43,680 --> 00:24:44,670
Then I'll arrange it.

607
00:24:51,250 --> 00:24:51,920
Mr. Li,

608
00:24:52,310 --> 00:24:53,510
the 3D simulation data

609
00:24:53,510 --> 00:24:54,390
is almost ready.

610
00:24:55,000 --> 00:24:56,950
Next, we'll be conducting olfactory

611
00:24:56,950 --> 00:24:57,910
and visual simulations.

612
00:24:58,120 --> 00:24:59,450
