613
00:25:00,280 --> 00:25:02,110
The detailed schedule will be sent to your inbox.

614
00:25:03,710 --> 00:25:04,360
Don't worry.

615
00:25:04,710 --> 00:25:06,830
I'll double-check everything.

616
00:25:06,890 --> 00:25:07,890
There won't be any mistakes.

617
00:25:08,640 --> 00:25:09,150
Alright.

618
00:25:10,330 --> 00:25:10,970
Come in.

619
00:25:12,650 --> 00:25:14,520
How is it? Finished?

620
00:25:15,430 --> 00:25:16,070
Take a look.

621
00:25:16,890 --> 00:25:17,720
Almost there.

622
00:25:18,830 --> 00:25:19,560
