623
00:25:19,810 --> 00:25:21,630
This is our first project in the company.

624
00:25:21,710 --> 00:25:22,630
It can't afford to go wrong.

625
00:25:25,830 --> 00:25:27,560
Also, we need to get Gu Nian busy,

626
00:25:27,960 --> 00:25:29,670
so she can taste the sweetness of success in her career.

627
00:25:30,110 --> 00:25:30,870
Only then will she realize that

628
00:25:30,870 --> 00:25:32,990
she can't just throw herself completely into Feng Huanan.

629
00:25:36,380 --> 00:25:37,230
Close the door.

630
00:25:42,120 --> 00:25:44,520
I heard you went home last night.

631
00:25:47,070 --> 00:25:47,790
I saw my mom.

632
00:25:50,590 --> 00:25:51,510
Gu Nian must have scolded me a lot, right?

633
00:25:52,910 --> 00:25:53,470
Not much.

634
00:25:55,080 --> 00:25:55,870
Well,

635
00:25:56,310 --> 00:25:59,350
somewhere between an earful and a total barrage of criticism.

636
00:26:01,710 --> 00:26:03,680
She said you got your mom to pick a side,

637
00:26:03,910 --> 00:26:05,070
dragging her into all of this.

638
00:26:07,270 --> 00:26:07,910
Let her say whatever she wants.

639
00:26:08,360 --> 00:26:09,100
As long as you can pull her

640
00:26:09,100 --> 00:26:10,230
back from the edge,

641
00:26:10,630 --> 00:26:11,600
she can scold me all she wants.

642
00:26:13,370 --> 00:26:14,550
How's it going with Feng Huanan?

643
00:26:14,750 --> 00:26:16,200
Did you find out who he's been connecting with?

644
00:26:16,590 --> 00:26:18,190
Guess who he's connected with?

645
00:26:18,380 --> 00:26:20,030
Jiang, don't keep me in suspense. Just tell me.

646
00:26:21,790 --> 00:26:22,670
Lyu Tu.

647
00:26:22,850 --> 00:26:25,030
Lyu Tu found him a partner.

648
00:26:25,480 --> 00:26:26,510
Lyu Tu is back?

649
00:26:26,690 --> 00:26:29,360
Lyu Tu is not the same person anymore.

650
00:26:29,380 --> 00:26:30,750
She's upgraded big time.

651
00:26:30,780 --> 00:26:32,570
Now she's working with all kinds of resources.

652
00:26:34,530 --> 00:26:36,580
Feng Huanan. Feng Huanan.

653
00:26:37,800 --> 00:26:38,910
I actually kind of admire him.

654
00:26:39,590 --> 00:26:41,590
He's always known what he wants.

655
00:26:41,990 --> 00:26:43,250
What I admire most is

656
00:26:43,710 --> 00:26:45,480
how he always manages to get people

657
00:26:45,480 --> 00:26:46,070
he's lost back into his life

658
00:26:46,100 --> 00:26:47,740
and make them follow his every word.

659
00:26:48,340 --> 00:26:50,290
If it weren't for his impatience

660
00:26:50,330 --> 00:26:51,530
and obsession with shortcuts,

661
00:26:52,040 --> 00:26:53,200
I honestly think he'd be

662
00:26:53,200 --> 00:26:53,960
a very successful person.

663
00:26:54,870 --> 00:26:55,960
So bitter.

664
00:26:56,550 --> 00:26:58,310
Why are you boosting his morale

665
00:26:58,310 --> 00:26:59,630
while taking away from your own?

666
00:27:00,020 --> 00:27:01,340
I'm just telling the truth.

667
00:27:01,360 --> 00:27:03,080
He really does work hard in certain areas.

668
00:27:03,830 --> 00:27:05,510
They're not as impressive as you make them sound.

669
00:27:06,210 --> 00:27:07,430
From what I know,

670
00:27:07,430 --> 00:27:09,430
their partner is also having second thoughts,

671
00:27:09,430 --> 00:27:10,750
so they did a background check

672
00:27:10,750 --> 00:27:11,860
on Feng Huanan

673
00:27:12,120 --> 00:27:13,190
and found out he doesn't have family connections

674
00:27:13,190 --> 00:27:13,880
or any backing.

675
00:27:14,320 --> 00:27:15,670
So, they're planning to have

676
00:27:15,670 --> 00:27:18,030
Feng Huanan put up some initial funding.

677
00:27:18,280 --> 00:27:20,670
They want to test his sincerity and ability,

678
00:27:21,040 --> 00:27:22,750
because, after all, no one wants to throw money down the drain.

679
00:27:23,310 --> 00:27:24,460
Well, in that case,

680
00:27:25,340 --> 00:27:27,080
Feng Huanan's motive for proposing to Gu Nian

681
00:27:27,080 --> 00:27:28,400
forms a perfect closed loop.

682
00:27:29,470 --> 00:27:31,600
He wants my mom to be the fall guy.

683
00:27:32,500 --> 00:27:33,140
Oh no.

684
00:27:34,430 --> 00:27:37,200
I heard your mom agreed to meet Feng Huanan.

685
00:27:38,500 --> 00:27:39,700
Your mom won't fall for it, will she?

686
00:27:39,870 --> 00:27:41,030
How is that possible?

687
00:27:41,510 --> 00:27:44,110
My mom agreeing to meet Feng Huanan is actually her being clever.

688
00:27:44,190 --> 00:27:45,240
She definitely took the things

689
00:27:45,240 --> 00:27:46,880
I said last night to heart.

690
00:27:47,160 --> 00:27:48,970
She knows that words alone won't work,

691
00:27:48,990 --> 00:27:50,350
and she can't go head-to-head with Gu Nian directly.

692
00:27:51,110 --> 00:27:53,280
So, she wants to personally help Gu Nian avoid the pitfalls.

693
00:27:53,330 --> 00:27:54,820
My mom and I have the same goal.

694
00:27:54,850 --> 00:27:55,810
That makes things much easier.

695
00:27:57,680 --> 00:27:58,560
Your mom is really wise.

696
00:27:59,880 --> 00:28:00,830
So, with you and your mom

697
00:28:01,170 --> 00:28:02,980
handling things for Gu Nian,

698
00:28:03,780 --> 00:28:05,040
and with me taking care of the project,

699
00:28:05,040 --> 00:28:05,920
we've got everything covered.

700
00:28:06,110 --> 00:28:08,270
You can just focus on what you need to do.

701
00:28:08,270 --> 00:28:10,460
We're like three strands of rope twisted together,

702
00:28:10,740 --> 00:28:11,380
unbeatable.

703
00:28:11,560 --> 00:28:11,880
I'm off.

704
00:28:11,910 --> 00:28:12,430
Jiang,

705
00:28:17,910 --> 00:28:18,720
thank you for your hard work.

706
00:28:20,180 --> 00:28:22,430
Well, you're both my male and female idol,

707
00:28:23,030 --> 00:28:24,870
both Gu Nian and my boss.

708
00:28:29,300 --> 00:28:30,600
It's no big deal.

709
00:28:31,270 --> 00:28:32,240
Next,

710
00:28:32,740 --> 00:28:33,850
I might have to play the bad guy.

711
00:28:34,120 --> 00:28:35,350
I'm going to have to be tough on Gu Nian.

712
00:28:35,690 --> 00:28:37,420
Please don't feel sorry for us.

713
00:28:37,850 --> 00:28:38,850
If you show any weakness,

714
00:28:39,670 --> 00:28:40,750
I'll soften up too.

715
00:28:41,860 --> 00:28:43,070
To be honest,

716
00:28:43,680 --> 00:28:46,030
I really don't want to see you two fight.

717
00:28:47,230 --> 00:28:48,430
But then again,

718
00:28:48,960 --> 00:28:49,840
I'm actually curious

719
00:28:49,840 --> 00:28:51,230
which one of you would win in a fight.

720
00:28:51,230 --> 00:28:53,150
Jiang, Jiang, you...

721
00:29:04,130 --> 00:29:04,810
Godmother,

722
00:29:07,250 --> 00:29:07,910
alright.

723
00:29:08,220 --> 00:29:09,490
Just send me the address.

724
00:29:10,470 --> 00:29:11,270
Okay, bye-bye.

725
00:29:24,170 --> 00:29:28,750
[Lyu Tu's back]
[If you really want to have Feng Huanan meet with Mom]
[You should first give Lyu Tu an explanation]

726
00:29:35,810 --> 00:29:37,090
Why don't you take it back?

727
00:29:37,860 --> 00:29:39,970
First come, first served. It's yours now.

728
00:29:41,270 --> 00:29:43,110
I don't want this dirty thing

729
00:29:43,110 --> 00:29:43,790
he gave me.

730
00:29:44,740 --> 00:29:46,220
But I bought it after all.

731
00:29:46,240 --> 00:29:47,070
It's not exactly dirty.

732
00:29:47,400 --> 00:29:48,630
He touched it.

733
00:29:48,630 --> 00:29:49,830
Doesn't that make it dirty?

734
00:29:49,830 --> 00:29:50,710
I don't want it.

735
00:29:51,150 --> 00:29:52,360
Fine, we both won't take it.

736
00:29:53,150 --> 00:29:53,470
No,

737
00:29:53,710 --> 00:29:55,070
I just don't get it.

738
00:29:55,270 --> 00:29:56,710
I've never been in a relationship,

739
00:29:56,710 --> 00:29:58,030
and I guess I was just misled,

740
00:29:58,030 --> 00:29:59,400
but you?

741
00:29:59,630 --> 00:30:00,870
If some random guy

742
00:30:00,870 --> 00:30:01,950
told me

743
00:30:01,950 --> 00:30:03,120
he'd take responsibility for me,

744
00:30:03,590 --> 00:30:04,910
I'd laugh

745
00:30:04,910 --> 00:30:06,470
and ignore him.

746
00:30:07,080 --> 00:30:08,430
But why did I take him seriously

747
00:30:08,930 --> 00:30:10,380
when he said it to me?

748
00:30:11,350 --> 00:30:13,590
I really… I'm such a fool.

749
00:30:13,680 --> 00:30:14,840
My brain must have been

750
00:30:14,860 --> 00:30:15,580
kicked by a donkey.

751
00:30:15,610 --> 00:30:16,890
I can't believe I fell for it.

752
00:30:39,690 --> 00:30:40,280
Nian.

753
00:30:43,220 --> 00:30:44,020
You're here.

754
00:30:44,200 --> 00:30:44,990
Please, have a seat.

755
00:30:48,470 --> 00:30:49,640
I don't know if your taste has changed.

756
00:30:49,680 --> 00:30:51,000
I ordered your old favorite drink.

757
00:30:51,510 --> 00:30:53,320
I don't drink that anymore.

758
00:30:53,450 --> 00:30:54,570
It's not good for the body if you have too much.

759
00:30:54,600 --> 00:30:55,400
You should drink less too.

760
00:30:55,990 --> 00:30:57,060
Hello, I'd like fruit and vegetable juice, please.

761
00:30:57,060 --> 00:30:57,610
Thank you.

762
00:30:57,650 --> 00:30:58,370
Okay.

763
00:31:04,340 --> 00:31:05,900
How did you know I was back?

764
00:31:09,210 --> 00:31:11,130
You left without a word. That was bad enough.

765
00:31:11,300 --> 00:31:12,630
But now you're back

766
00:31:12,630 --> 00:31:13,680
