767
00:31:13,880 --> 00:31:15,640
I'm not avoiding you.

768
00:31:15,640 --> 00:31:17,840
I've just been busy making money.

769
00:31:22,410 --> 00:31:25,850
It seems like you're going to be the first to achieve

770
00:31:26,580 --> 00:31:27,980
the dreams we all talked about back then.

771
00:31:28,520 --> 00:31:29,320
How so?

772
00:31:29,780 --> 00:31:31,940
You still haven't found your prince charming?

773
00:31:35,180 --> 00:31:37,170
Aren't you with Su Yin?

774
00:31:39,360 --> 00:31:40,320
No.

775
00:31:40,870 --> 00:31:42,030
He and I are colleagues.

776
00:31:42,230 --> 00:31:42,870
And there's also Jiang Ze.

777
00:31:42,870 --> 00:31:44,270
We're in the same company.

778
00:31:44,510 --> 00:31:45,630
We're working on a project together now.

779
00:31:49,640 --> 00:31:51,870
It's still the same old faces, huh?

780
00:31:53,860 --> 00:31:54,570
That's nice.

781
00:32:04,150 --> 00:32:05,550
Here's your juice.

782
00:32:05,580 --> 00:32:06,340
Great, thank you.

783
00:32:24,130 --> 00:32:24,860
Tu,

784
00:32:25,870 --> 00:32:28,230
