789
00:32:39,910 --> 00:32:41,320
Do you still love him now?

790
00:32:48,940 --> 00:32:49,750
Love?

791
00:32:51,630 --> 00:32:54,190
Love is so complicated.

792
00:32:54,790 --> 00:32:56,950
There's too much to decode.

793
00:32:57,580 --> 00:32:59,260
You know

794
00:32:59,390 --> 00:33:00,640
