795
00:33:02,420 --> 00:33:04,330
When have I ever loved anyone?

796
00:33:05,090 --> 00:33:06,620
I only love myself.

797
00:33:34,650 --> 00:33:35,740
Tu, I'm sorry.

798
00:33:35,980 --> 00:33:37,330
I broke our promise.

799
00:33:38,600 --> 00:33:40,240
I'm back with Huanan.

800
00:33:42,550 --> 00:33:43,550
He proposed to me.
